  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Children diagnosed with Juvenile Idiopathic Arthritis, followed in dept of pediatric
        rheumatology, Aarhus University Hospital, Skejby
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Juvenile idiopathic arthritis: Oligoarticular, polyarticular or systemic onset type.

          -  Informed consent from parents

          -  between 5-15 years of age

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Other diagnoses that involves bones or cartilage

          -  Intraarticular steroid injections within 1 month of the trial investigation
      </textblock>
